title: ARY News Headlines |PM Khan telephones Erdogan| 7PM | 11 Oct 2019
text:
PM Khan expresses dismay over lack of int’l media coverage on Kashmir crisis.

Fazal’s Azadi March to go in vain, says Fayyaz-ul-Hassan Chohan.

Million of Kashmiris to take to streets after curfew lifted: PM Imran.

Accountability Court adjourns LNG case hearing until Oct 28.

‘Pakistanis awaiting to welcome you’: PM Khan telephones Erdogan.

Court grants physical remand of Nawaz Sharif in Chaudhry Sugar Mills case.

Dubai land department to share details of properties with Pakistani owners: Zaidi.

Federal cabinet session summoned on October 16.
